quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  43,23,"Wakathalika ma arsalnamin qablika fee qaryatin min natheerin illa qalamutrafooha inna wajadna abaanaAAala ommatin wa-inna AAala atharihimmuqtadoon"
  43,24,"Qala awa law ji/tukum bi-ahdamimma wajadtum AAalayhi abaakum qalooinna bima orsiltum bihi kafiroon"
  43,25,"Fantaqamna minhum fanthurkayfa kana AAaqibatu almukaththibeen"
  43,26,"Wa-ith qala ibraheemuli-abeehi waqawmihi innanee baraon mimma taAAbudoon"
  43,27,"Illa allathee fataraneefa-innahu sayahdeen"
  43,28,"WajaAAalaha kalimatan baqiyatanfee AAaqibihi laAAallahum yarjiAAoon"
  43,29,"Bal mattaAAtu haola-i waabaahumhatta jaahumu alhaqqu warasoolunmubeen"
  43,30,"Walamma jaahumu alhaqquqaloo hatha sihrun wa-inna bihi kafiroon"
  43,31,"Waqaloo lawla nuzzila hathaalqur-anu AAala rajulin mina alqaryatayni AAatheem"
  43,32,"Ahum yaqsimoona rahmata rabbika nahnuqasamna baynahum maAAeeshatahum fee alhayatiaddunya warafaAAna baAAdahum fawqabaAAdin darajatin liyattakhitha baAAduhumbaAAdan sukhriyyan warahmatu rabbika khayrun mimmayajmaAAoon"
  43,33,"Walawla an yakoona annasuommatan wahidatan lajaAAalna liman yakfuru birrahmanilibuyootihim suqufan min fiddatin wamaAAarijaAAalayha yathharoon"
